      "6-mer tokenization outperforms single-nucleotide and BPE for autoregressive genomic LM",
      "GENERator-1B surpasses Evo2-1B on sequence recovery; 3B approaches Evo2-7B, with ~19-44x faster generation",
      "Functional (gene-centric) pre-training beats indiscriminate all-sequence training on downstream tasks",
      "Prompt-guided CRE design produces enhancers/silencers exceeding natural activity range (UMI-STARR-seq validated)"
